title: SweetMook - Lord of the Dung - Cow Dung Eating
description:
This is "The Lord of the Dung,"  from the defunct sweetmook.com website.  The content of this movie is almost unbelievable.  Two hot Thai girls, 19-20 years old, are at a farm.  One of them proceeds to give cunnilingus to the cow, after which the cow takes a cow-sized shit right into her face.  After gathering all of the dung into a large tin pan, the two girls sit down for a nice lunch break.  They proceed to swallow the entire pan full of cow dung.  One of the girls, (stage name "Poo"), is particularly enthusiastic, chewing and swallowing the cow dung as if it were a normal thing to eat.  The other girl, "Mook,"  has a harder time, but manages to swallow a few mouthfuls.  As you can imagine, another pan is nearby for the purposes of catching vomit.

This is another movie from sweetmook.com that must be seen to be believed.
